snippet.title: Sky Taxi 1 (Windows game 2009)
snippet.description:
Ski Taxi 1 is a Russian platform game made by Alawar Games, Sky Bros (Alexander & Michael Makovsky).
You should free fairies in a case and go to the exit.
You can kill enemies using treading. (can't use weapons)
